This seems to be fixed now (checked VirusTotal and my own VM): https://www.virustotal.com/en/file/1b6f8899408b88059ff568890cd33eb64d7be73ff1ea22829ba34eb244d63f0d/analysis/

Anyone else able to verify? I am showing definition version 160212-1. Right-click the icon in the system tray and choose "About Avast" then look at the "Virus definitions version." If it's showing an older version, try updating manually: right-click the tray icon again and choose "Update -> Engine and virus definitions."

To really verify you will unfortunately need to remove your exemption, which may of course quarantine the Launcher again if it's not really fixed. {{item:3070}}
